										</figure>
										<span>John Doe, via <a href="#" class="twitter">Twitter</a></span>
										<blockquote>
											<p>&ldquo;Separated they live in Bookmarksgrove right at the coast of the Semantics, a large language ocean.&rdquo;</p>
										</blockquote>
									</div>
